Date of Birth: May 4, 1865<br/>
Birthplace: Dublin, Ireland<br/>
Ordained apostle: October 12, 1933<br/>
Death: January 21, 1947<br/>
<br/>
Born May 4, 1865, at Dublin, Dublin Co., Ireland, to John Callis and Susanna Charlotte Quillam. Ordained apostle Oct. 12, 1933, by Heber J. Grant, at age 68; died Jan. 21, 1947, in Jacksonville, Duval Co., Florida, at age 81.